  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b95\u0bc6\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fewer than a thousand private buses ply today - Kemunu",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Private Bus Owners Association of Sri Lanka has warned that the bus service may be completely suspended from today due to the fuel crisis.",
        "Kemunuwijayaratna said that all the private buses are stuck in the fuel line and even 1000 buses cannot be put into service today.",
        "He said that thousands of people are trapped in the crisis without any other type of transport facilities as the bus is an alternative means of transport for a large number of people."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Fewer than a thousand",
          "label": "CARDINAL"
